      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition and has been maintained to the highest standards. The exterior paint is flawless, displaying a deep, mirror-like shine without any scratches, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is in pristine condition, with the upholstery and trim looking exactly as they did when the car first left the dealership. Mechanically, it is perfect, offering a smooth and powerful driving experience that reflects its low-wear history and meticulous care. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been preserved in like-new condition.",
