    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained, making it a reliable and attractive choice for its next owner. The engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts precisely, and all major mechanical systems are in solid working order. While there may be some light cosmetic wear consistent with careful use, the interior is clean and the exterior retains a great finish. You can expect a dependable driving experience with no immediate maintenance needs.",
