    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride? I'm parting with my car and it's been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been well-cared for, so it's ready to hit the road with its next owner immediately. It runs smoothly and looks great\u2014perfect for your daily commute or a fun weekend road trip. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so come check it out and see for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
