      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2008 Porsche Cayman S, featuring the 3.4L M97 flat-six engine paired with a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. This mid-engine platform offers unparalleled balance and a low center of gravity. The vehicle is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), providing adaptive damping for various road surfaces. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive inspection of the cooling system and a fresh oil service using high-zinc lubricants to maintain internal component longevity. The braking system utilizes four-piston monoblock calipers over cross-drilled rotors, ensuring consistent thermal management. While the exterior shows minor road-derived character, the drivetrain remains mechanically sound with linear power delivery and a taut chassis response.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
